            <title>[JDK-8316659] assert(LockingMode != LM_LIGHTWEIGHT || flag == CCR0) failed: bad condition register</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8316659</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>We&amp;#39;re running into the assertion (macroAssembler_ppc.cpp:2183) since &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8315880&quot; title=&quot;Change LockingMode default from LM_LEGACY to LM_LIGHTWEIGHT&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8315880&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8315880&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. The native wrapper doesn&amp;#39;t use the correct ConditionRegister for the new locking mode:&lt;br/&gt;
